{"tid":1494712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣海報是否應該「光復香港，時代革命」融入到五大訴求？","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T18:25:10.000Z","uid":107611,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"74e91ec0f8fe29a7205afe8ce9a1b9d573af9fbb","tid":1494712,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"「光復香港」=  將香港帶返去禮崩樂壞之前的時候。<br />\n- 撤回送中惡法<br />\n- 設立獨立調查委員會，追究警隊濫權濫暴<br />\n- 撤銷對反修例抗爭者的檢控<br />\n- 撤回暴動定性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「時代革命」=  令這個時代大改變的大革新。<br />\n- 真&bull;雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*係可以更有效令普羅市民接受「革命」呢一詞，嚮呢次運動嘅用意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家意下如何？"},{"pid":"3fbaf1503a2913b955d83da8534d805a255128f5","tid":1494712,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:02:10.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"c1b7133219f6a64e54609b7edaf085ea27045546","tid":1494712,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"所以文宣最低部都加呢句"},{"pid":"2899d835113318f5ecdcf98bebf974f85d1b79b5","tid":1494712,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1b7133219f6a64e54609b7edaf085ea27045546","tid":1494712,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"所以文宣最低部都加呢句"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:06:29.000Z","msg":"已經結合咗？"},{"pid":"248c1d882f90f1fd1c4dd2db2b0a781908e6a3c3","tid":1494712,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2899d835113318f5ecdcf98bebf974f85d1b79b5","tid":1494712,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1b7133219f6a64e54609b7edaf085ea27045546","tid":1494712,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"所以文宣最低部都加呢句"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:06:29.000Z","msg":"已經結合咗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:07:09.000Z","msg":"希望姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fabff0aa72